Crypto Wallet Safety : Don't Get Robbed ! Cold Wallets Are Your Fort Knox If you're not trading it , stash it in a cold wallet . Think of it as your personal Fort Knox but way easier to set up . Hot Wallets for the Quick Draw For coins you're actively trading , a hot wallet does the trick . Just remember , it's like carrying cash ; don't stuff it too full . Double-Check Addresses Sending crypto ? Double , triple-check the address . Mess this up , and your money's gone faster than a pint at happy hour . 2FA : The Bouncer for Your Account Two-Factor Authentication ( 2FA ) is a must . It's the bouncer for your crypto club , only letting you in . Beware of Phishers Watch out for fake websites and apps . Always check the URL and app reviews .
